<pb n="0966b" ed="T" id="T14.0582.0966b"/>
<lb n="0966b01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0966b02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 582</head>
<lb n="0966b03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說孫多耶致經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0966b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0966b05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">吳月支<note n="0966017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">國居士＝優婆塞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">國居士＝優婆塞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966017"><lem wit="【大】">國居士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">優婆塞</rdg></app>支謙譯</byline>
<lb n="0966b06" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0966b0601">聞如是：</p><p id="pT14p0966b0604" place="inline">一時佛在舍衛國，行在祇樹給孤獨
<lb n="0966b07" ed="T"/>園，除饉甚眾，佛為說經。</p><p id="pT14p0966b0710" place="inline">時有梵志，名孫多
<lb n="0966b08" ed="T"/>耶致，望見佛，即住<note n="0966018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝委【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0966018"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">委</rdg></app>杖，吐舌念曰：「吾日
<lb n="0966b09" ed="T"/>三浴，<note n="0966019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">啖＝噉【宮】</note><app n="0966019"><lem wit="【大】">啖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">噉</rdg></app>果，飲水，不受人施。吾行勝沙門行。
<lb n="0966b10" ed="T"/>子曹甘食、好衣、溫蓐，訛賢非真，不如吾道也。」</p>
<lb n="0966b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0966b1101">佛知梵志心之所存，告諸沙門曰：「夫人為行，
<lb n="0966b12" ed="T"/>有二十一惡，不得美食、好衣：志在<note n="0966020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬泆＝婬&CB00105;【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0966020"><lem wit="【大】">婬泆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">婬&CB00105;</rdg></app>；志
<lb n="0966b13" ed="T"/>在瞋恚；志在愚癡；志在睡臥；志在<note n="0966021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">凝＝疑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">凝＝疑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966021"><lem wit="【大】">凝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">疑</rdg></app>結，
<lb n="0966b14" ed="T"/>謂無應儀；志在貢高；志在憍慢；志在嫉&CB00107;；
<lb n="0966b15" ed="T"/>志在慳貪；志在兇虐，無惻隱心；志在虛偽，
<lb n="0966b16" ed="T"/>內外相違；志在不慚，內無愧心；志在穢行，
<lb n="0966b17" ed="T"/>不自羞鄙；志在彼惡而不自見；志在<note n="0966022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔婬〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔婬〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966022"><lem wit="【大】">婬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>泆，
<lb n="0966b18" ed="T"/>言不歎<note n="0966023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貞＋（良）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貞＋（良）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966023"><lem wit="【大】">貞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">貞良</rdg></app>；志在交話，讒成二惡；志在會&CB00508;，
<lb n="0966b19" ed="T"/>不釋兩諍；志在無禮，自可不謙；志在遂非，
<lb n="0966b20" ed="T"/>不受賢諫；志在不孝，滅慈好逆；志好邪道，
<lb n="0966b21" ed="T"/>供奉妖蠱，家財虛竭，令親困窮，不覺非常，
<lb n="0966b22" ed="T"/>不歸三尊，美食、好衣從欲奢華。以斯二十
<lb n="0966b23" ed="T"/>一惡，穢亂其心。猶<note n="0966024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">潔＝&CB00626;【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0966024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">潔＝&CB00626;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0966024"><lem wit="【大】">潔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&CB00626;</rdg></app>污垢，染之為色，萬無
<lb n="0966b24" ed="T"/><note n="0966025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一益＝益一【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一益＝益一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966025"><lem wit="【大】">一益</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">益一</rdg></app>。懷斯眾惡，死入地獄、餓鬼、畜生，其
<lb n="0966b25" ed="T"/><note n="0966026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痛＝猶【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0966026"><lem wit="【大】">痛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">猶</rdg></app>難量。</p><p id="pT14p0966b2504" place="inline">「沙門&CB00418;佛明戒，棄故自新，練情滅
<lb n="0966b26" ed="T"/>欲，內外清淨。又如淨<app type="＊" source="0966024"><lem wit="【大】">潔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&CB00626;</rdg></app>，染即成色，為眾所
<lb n="0966b27" ed="T"/>觀。沙門&CB00418;明，行高智足。天下供奉衣、食、殿
<lb n="0966b28" ed="T"/>舍，受之無尤，施者福大。進行禪定，獲溝港、
<lb n="0966b29" ed="T"/>頻來、不還、應儀，人亦聞之。沙門雖未得道，
<pb n="0966c" ed="T" id="T14.0582.0966c"/>
<lb n="0966c01" ed="T"/>明佛經義，執心端正，孝順經教，弘慈<note n="0966027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">普育＝育物【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">普育＝育物【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966027"><lem wit="【大】">普育</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">育物</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0966c02" ed="T"/>潤逮群生，恕己安彼，視怨若子。見女人來，
<lb n="0966c03" ed="T"/>待之以妹。若&CB00418;窮苦，當念地獄、餓鬼、畜生，
<lb n="0966c04" ed="T"/>願令群生身安意喜，得逢三寶，垢除冥滅，
<lb n="0966c05" ed="T"/>心淨見明，還於本無，永康無極。志行如斯，
<lb n="0966c06" ed="T"/>美食、好衣終始無罪。群生本性，貪婬、瞋恚、
<lb n="0966c07" ed="T"/>愚癡、嫉&CB00107;，濁中之濁、冥中之冥者。沙門心開
<lb n="0966c08" ed="T"/>受明，癡垢都寂。雖處穢世，猶蓮華居夫泥中，
<lb n="0966c09" ed="T"/>泥不能<note n="0966028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">染＝污【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">染＝污【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966028"><lem wit="【大】">染</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">污</rdg></app>華，受施無罪。夫懷三毒、十惡不
<lb n="0966c10" ed="T"/>除，恣心從欲，諂欺求潤，不奉佛戒，寧吞熱鐵，
<lb n="0966c11" ed="T"/>飲<note n="0966029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洋＝烊【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0966029"><lem wit="【大】">洋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">烊</rdg></app>銅。斯死須臾穢濁受施，死入太山，飲
<lb n="0966c12" ed="T"/>銅，食炭，其年難計矣。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c1209" place="inline">梵志前白佛言：「吾欲
<lb n="0966c13" ed="T"/>去浴，有溪名<note n="0966030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好首＝好前【宮】</note><app n="0966030"><lem wit="【大】">好首</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">好前</rdg></app>。夫入中浴者，意之穢垢，
<lb n="0966c14" ed="T"/>隨水流漂。自聞父教，<note n="0966031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾＝言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吾＝言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966031"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">言</rdg></app>日三浴。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c1413" place="inline">佛告梵志：
<lb n="0966c15" ed="T"/>「斯土多溪，人入中浴可得獲度苦乎？千浴
<lb n="0966c16" ed="T"/>之人可除身垢，奈心垢何？吾諸沙門<note n="0966032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斷求＝斷末【宮】</note><app n="0966032"><lem wit="【大】">斷求</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">斷末</rdg></app>
<lb n="0966c17" ed="T"/>念空，不願三界，心垢寂滅，以得淨道。汝從
<lb n="0966c18" ed="T"/>何師？受法水浴，去心垢乎？」</p><p id="pT14p0966c1811" place="inline">對曰：「吾父云爾。」</p>
<lb n="0966c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT14p0966c1901">佛言：「若父得道不？」</p><p id="pT14p0966c1908" place="inline">對曰：「不也。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c1912" place="inline">佛言：「吾道從
<lb n="0966c20" ed="T"/>心出，心端，志淨，乃得道耳。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2011" place="inline">梵志長跪陳白：
<lb n="0966c21" ed="T"/>「吾向拄杖吐舌，但為狂愚耳。今聞佛經，心
<lb n="0966c22" ed="T"/>始醒寤。猶冥中有燈火，始今有目矣。乞為
<lb n="0966c23" ed="T"/>沙門，願佛哀納！」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2307" place="inline">佛言：「若有<note n="0966033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＝觀【宮】＊</note><app n="0966033"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">觀</rdg></app>，報之。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2314" place="inline">對曰：
<lb n="0966c24" ed="T"/>「無<app type="＊" source="0966033"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">觀</rdg></app>。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2403" place="inline">佛言：「沙門來。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2408" place="inline">即成沙門已，於樹下
<lb n="0966c25" ed="T"/>坐，<note n="0966034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0966034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0966034"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">唯</rdg></app>二十一事，去諸欲念，<note n="0966035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">霍然＝庸然【宋】，膚然【宮】</note><note n="0966035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">霍然＝庸然【宋】，＝膚然【宮】</note><app n="0966035"><lem wit="【大】">霍然</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">庸然</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">膚然</rdg></app>無想，即
<lb n="0966c26" ed="T"/>得應儀道，<note n="0966036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">赴＝起【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">赴＝起【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966036"><lem wit="【大】">赴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">起</rdg></app>至佛所，以頭面著佛足言：「今
<lb n="0966c27" ed="T"/>盲者得視，狂病得愈。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2709" place="inline">佛言：「斯道佳耶？汝道
<lb n="0966c28" ed="T"/>佳乎？」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2803" place="inline">對曰：「眾道皆邪，唯佛道正。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2813" place="inline">佛告諸沙
<lb n="0966c29" ed="T"/>門：「熟<app type="＊" source="0966034"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">唯</rdg></app>二十一事，道可得矣。」</p><p id="pT14p0966c2912" place="inline">諸沙門聞經
<pb n="0967a" ed="T" id="T14.0582.0967a"/>
<lb n="0967a01" ed="T"/>歡喜，作禮而退。</p></div1>
<lb n="0967a02" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說孫多耶致經</jhead></juan>
